txt.en: 'A villager was out foraging near Telperiën's Wall and reported seeing Umbari strangers digging for artifacts. These items of antiquity belong to the people of Ambarûl. It is not a free-for-all for outsiders to come and take these things and sell them in foreign lands. Go there and put a stop to this theft by any means necessary.'
You have dealt with the thieving Corsairs stealing artifacts from the ruins of Telperiën's Wall. Return with the Dumûri scout to report your success.
There is no twist in this mission.
Umbari Corsairs are stealing artifacts from the Ambarûli side of Telperiën's Wall.
'Thank you for stopping these thieves from stealing that which belongs to all of our people.'
'Your mission is to stop thieving Corsairs from stealing artifacts from the ruins of Telperiën's Wall.'
Your mission is to stop thieving Corsairs from stealing artifacts from the ruins of Telperiën's Wall, by any means necessary.\n\nTalk to Khâdamul when you are ready to travel.
